reviews.text: We booked a private function room and great way to spend the arvo. at the races. Good smorgasbord variety of food, plenty of drink and always nice to leave the place cash positive!
haha.. Friend booking for birthday lunch. 😊

英倫風格～喜馬當先～

就係馬場站，一入馬場行幾分鐘就到啦，都算容易搵到。餐廳係英倫風格，職員全都有格仔風，加上優雅的裝修，極有風格。周圍都有直播賽馬賽事，喜歡戶外，仲可以到露台睇添。
餐廳係半自助餐形式，甜品，沙律菜，刺身，湯等。主菜就點了脆燒豬手伴燴甜酸蘿蔔配英式芥茉。

脆燒豬手伴燴甜酸蘿蔔配英式芥茉
豬手既皮燒得夠香夠脆，又唔會好鹹，肉質軟稔。不過對於愛瘦既女士來講會帶點油。信義妹新覺得油脂夾雜肉，口感豐腴。覺得油可以用甜酸蘿蔔拌食一解油膩。
英式芥茉無咩特別。

刺身有三文魚，吞拿魚，魷魚，北寄貝。冷盤有凍蝦，翡翠螺，青口，蝦彈牙又帶膏既甘香，呢個要 encore 幾次啊！

甜品有泡芙，批，蛋糕，雪糕，生果等。最欣賞係香蕉蛋糕，唔太甜又唔會一 Pat Pat, 有啲咬口。藍莓批都讚不絶口，可以用雪糕相伴啊！

有杯 Special drink, 飲品帶酸，塊餅偏甜，個別食都不太好，兩者一起就甜酸度剛好啦！

最後，有杯熱檸水消消滯。

裝修環境好靚，露台睇馬一流，好清楚
主菜魚幾好味，反而牛就麻麻地
裝修靚, 服務好, buffet食物選擇唔算多, 但質素唔錯.

reviews.text: The Sha Tin Racecourse will provide memorable experiences for members and guests. Firstly, the racecourse itself provides entertainment for horse racing. This location hosts daytime weekly horse races and is a good place for people to visit for fun. Secondly, the clubhouse there is luxurious and provides a variety of facilities and services such as Children’s Playroom, Swimming Pool, Tennis Court and way more. There are also two restaurants, Chinese and Western, at the club. The food there is good too. Overall, this is a place that visitors will enjoy thoroughly.

Very pleasant day spent at the races. Customer service counters were very helpful with teaching us how to place bets. Large air-conditioned lobby with lots of locals watching the big screens. Bring your own pen for writing. Food is a bit expensive too, so eat before coming if you don’t want to pay premium prices for regular food.

My first time to watch a live horse racing, the experience was wonderful. I can feel the exhilaration in the air when the race starts. You bet the Hong Kongers love this sport. You can also try your luck here, just follow what the locals do.

The place is showing it's age. The clubhouse... Did they ever renovate in 40 years? It looks so 80's. C'mon, it's one of the most prestige club in Hong Kong. The restaurants in member's area，compared to those in modern 5 star hotels are clearly no match. Oh, the public area... Some places really looks so declined.
Good experience! At the desk they explained me every thing o need to know about horse racing. Great place and good beerz too
